  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00881', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲：不惑之年。乙：花甲之年。丙：而立之年。丁：花信之年。 以上詞語皆與年齡有關，依年紀由小到大排列，順序是：', '["乙丙甲丁", "丙甲丁乙", "丁甲乙丙", "丁丙甲乙"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00882', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關「頭髮」的成語，何者正確？', '["「童山濯濯」形容頭髮烏黑濃密", "「擢髮難數」形容掉落的頭髮不計其數", "「櫛風沐雨」形容不顧風雨辛苦奔波", "「吐哺握髮」形容生重病的樣子"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00883', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列與「桃」有關成語的解釋，何者正確？', '["桃夭及時－祝賀女子出嫁", "桃李滿門－比喻禮尚往來", "桃李不言－喻贈人桃李不如贈人以言", "桃羞杏讓－比喻互相頂替或代人受過"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00884', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關書函用語的說明，何者最正確？', '["寫給老師的信自稱「晚生」", "信中提到自己過世的親人應加「前」字", "信中提到他人父親，應稱「令尊」", "寫給長官的信，信封收信人名下應寫「敬啟」"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00885', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於應用文書的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["啟事是用於各機關間的非公開文書", "對長輩或是不熟的人，不宜使用便條", "訃聞是將人死亡的消息，通知親友的應用文書", "喜帖常見「闔第光臨」，是請賓客全家參加婚宴的敬辭"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00886', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列應用文字使用正確的是：', '["寫信給師長的提稱語：函丈", "謙稱自己過世的父親：家父", "堂兄結婚的祝福語：于歸誌喜", "朋友榮升的祝賀詞：儀型足式"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00887', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '「四角尖尖草縛腰，浪蕩鍋中走一遭」是某個傳統節日的習俗，下列選項何者與題目所吟詠的節日不同？', '["競渡岸傍人挂錦，採芳城上女遺簪", "不效艾符趨習俗，但祈蒲酒話昇平", "錢浮蓮沼形猶小，日映花磚影最長", "包中香黍分邊角，綵線剪就交絨索"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00888', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '朱熹編纂之「四子書」內容為何？', '["大學、中庸、論語、孟子", "孫子、荀子、老子、孟子", "荀子、孟子、孝經、詩經", "易經、尚書、詩經、莊子"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00889', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '《荀子．勸學》：「騏驥一躍，不能十步；駑馬十駕，功在不舍。」下列選項，與上文旨意不同的是：', '["千里之行，始於足下", "譬如平地，雖覆一簣，進，吾往也", "君子不為小人匈匈也輟行", "人一能之，己百之；人十能之，己千之"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-acfc4025-moex-00890', 'elementary-acfc4025', 'elementary-acfc4025-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-acfc4025-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列選項，何者不是歌詠諸葛亮的詩句？', '["至今出師表，讀之淚沾胸", "擊筑飲美酒，劍歌易水湄", "三顧頻煩天下計，兩朝開濟老臣心", "運移漢祚終難復，志決身殲軍務勞"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "515", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL)
